    "key": "Tbl_Unit_Desc_142",
    "english": "Demon, a member of the onis. Adjusting to the culture and life of the human world, they serve as mercenaries in the underworld. Wearing clothes and acting like a Sengoku Era samurai in Japan, they swing tachis swiftly, performing a precise attack.",
